{"tid":1434351,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今天不小心把心愛的鼻毛拔斷了","createTime":"2019-08-08T18:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T16:19:11.000Z","uid":136738,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"68e6a4a1b85c231b124b7c58d43d30f310d645f9","tid":1434351,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:00:39.000Z","msg":"今天不小心把心愛的鼻毛拔斷了<br />\n事後我用了十五分鐘去細心欣賞<br />\n發現拔斷了的鼻碎毛<br />\n竟然比起平日那個形態更美<br />\n然後我再用了十分鐘去洗乾淨手<br />\n再為其拍照　這短短的三十分鐘<br />\n算是今天我思緒最安穩的時間<br />\n拔斷了的鼻毛<br />\n是我今天看過最美好的東西<br />\n而我屁股著地的那一聲<br />\n是聽過最美好的聲音<br />\n原來人生覺得最爛的事情<br />\n也未必是最糟<br />\n因為最糟的<br />\n可能一直就在眼前而未曾發現<br />\n又或者根本就是自己<br />\n我想我找到了答案"},{"pid":"046735a24adb3beb1d03e47cf76441db78a0b97b","tid":1434351,"uid":38293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4f084eced199a3e45aecf4aca1b11080d3e38e","tid":1434351,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:01:05.000Z","msg":"爆裂鼻毛拳"},{"pid":"e0e60151d2c786a1e21a5c3ff15af422497c15c5","tid":1434351,"uid":48358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01GfFkH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01GfFkH.png&h=126a7f1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d30ca598bed901dba2b668b98db0ccfd810ad4b","tid":1434351,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da4f084eced199a3e45aecf4aca1b11080d3e38e","tid":1434351,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:01:05.000Z","msg":"爆裂鼻毛拳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":